{"tid":1892163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯衛生部聲明：從未將武漢肺炎定性為人工合成病毒","createTime":"2020-02-22T10:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T10:23:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"9228156b1a8597799daa95c836e7f7387fc9fde6","tid":1892163,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T10:48:08.000Z","msg":"2020年2月22日更新<br />\n<br />\n18：00【俄羅斯衛生部聲明：從未將武漢肺炎定性為人工合成病毒】近日有消息傳出，俄羅斯聯邦衛生部發佈的《新冠狀病毒（2019-nCoV）感染預防、診斷和治療方法臨時方法建議》中，指稱武漢肺炎的病毒是「人工合成」。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯聯邦衛生部發言人澄清，「俄羅斯聯邦衛生部《新冠狀病毒感染預防、診斷和治療臨時方法指南》中，從未指出病毒是人工的」，並強調俄國衛生部所發布的《指南》，僅是為了向居民傳達防疫措施，屬於通用文件，原文沒有出現任何「人工合成」字詞。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://invest.hket.com/article/2569806/【財經直播】俄羅斯衛生部聲明：從未將武漢肺炎定性為人工合成病毒</code></pre>"},{"pid":"0d7e69101ac5d587077e10c10d9e803a9f6e40f3","tid":1892163,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08b4990de820965d915ca9e4e80219a1fd908e7","tid":1892163,"uid":253016,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:40:38.000Z","msg":"買左幾多桶油?"},{"pid":"e2d19ad0553ebb935bbe768231cdf9270494f6ab","tid":1892163,"uid":88743,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:41:54.000Z","msg":"我見連登前兩日無source 所以都估到係流料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad80dd368824d9310360c943619dcbc2c6a9c52","tid":1892163,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:44:10.000Z","msg":"哩吓係柒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［重要］FC: &lsquo;俄官方確認武漢肺炎病毒係人工造成&rsquo;哩單新聞，極可能係fake news<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1892097\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1892097</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}